category: Ruby
requires: ruby
sdesc: "Ruby documentation formatter"
ldesc: "RD is multipurpose documentation format created for 
documentating Ruby and output of Ruby world. You can embed RD into Ruby 
script. And RD have neat syntax which help you to read document in Ruby 
script. On the other hand, RD have a feature for class reference. RDtool 
is one of frontends of formatter for RD. This package provides rd2 
command."
